{"tid":2250300,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 11名「垂釣發燒友」港珠澳大橋橋墩垂釣被拘  嚴重者會被內地拘留","createTime":"2020-10-20T04:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T10:54:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"db1c651d2802e4eaec38fd8332d1831dc8d3bd61","tid":2250300,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:21:51.000Z","msg":"近日有11名「垂釣發燒友」擅自坐船到港珠澳大橋的橋墩上釣魚，內地海事執法人員與珠海市公安局水域治安管理支隊開展聯合執法，帶走全部非法垂釣人員，收繳26根魚竿和5箱漁獲。<br />\n<br />\n執法人員表示，根據《中華人民共和國治安管理處罰法》有關規定，船舶擅自進入、停靠國家禁止或限制進入的水域或者島嶼，對船舶負責人及有關責任人員罰款500元至1000元人民幣，嚴重者會被拘留5天以下；進入港珠澳大橋一級警戒區橋墩釣魚、在非通航橋孔滯留等行為都是禁止的，垂釣行為不僅嚴重影響青州航道的通航環境，還危及大橋和垂釣人員自身安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20201019/s00004/1603116276549/11釣友擅登港珠澳大橋橋墩垂釣被拘-檢26魚竿5箱漁獲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20201019%2Fs00004%2F1603116276549%2F11%E9%87%A3%E5%8F%8B%E6%93%85%E7%99%BB%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E6%A9%8B%E5%A2%A9%E5%9E%82%E9%87%A3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%98-%E6%AA%A226%E9%AD%9A%E7%AB%BF5%E7%AE%B1%E6%BC%81%E7%8D%B2&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=ba3e69a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20201019%2Fs00004%2F1603116276549%2F11%E9%87%A3%E5%8F%8B%E6%93%85%E7%99%BB%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E6%A9%8B%E5%A2%A9%E5%9E%82%E9%87%A3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%98-%E6%AA%A226%E9%AD%9A%E7%AB%BF5%E7%AE%B1%E6%BC%81%E7%8D%B2&h=33cadfa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20201019/s00004/1603116276549/11釣友擅登港珠澳大橋橋墩垂釣被拘-檢26魚竿5箱漁獲</a>"},{"pid":"ff16f3fdf5c16634c0ff661057084ae1f8133edc","tid":2250300,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lo